ites to the cart, and proceed to checkout. You’ll receive an order confirmation email once payment is complete.<\/p>"}},"frequently_asked_question_MneHrw":{"type":"frequently_asked_question","settings":{"icon":"none","another_icon":"","custom_icon":"","heading":"Can I order in bulk?","row_content":"<p>Yes! We offer bulk purchases for selected products. Please contact our customer service team for bulk pricing or special requests.<\/p>"}},"frequently_asked_question_i8HCPg":{"type":"frequently_asked_question","settings":{"icon":"none","another_icon":"","custom_icon":"","heading":"How do I know if an item is in stock?","row_content":"<p>You will be able to add in-stock products to your cart. If an item is temporarily out of stock, it will be clearly marked as 'out of stock', and you can choose to be notified by email when it’s back.<\/p>"}},"frequently_asked_question_GnfFKi":{"type":"frequently_asked_question","settings":{"icon":"none","another_icon":"","custom_icon":"","heading":"Do you have expiry dates on products?","row_content":"<p>Absolutely. All our products are fresh and have clearly printed expiry or best-before dates. We do not sell expired goods.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["frequently_asked_question_XnGxjH","frequently_asked_question_MneHrw","frequently_asked_question_i8HCPg","frequently_asked_question_GnfFKi"],"name":"t:sections.question_and_answer.name","settings":{"heading":"ORDERS & PRODUCTS","highlight_type":"underline","heading_size":100,"heading_tag":"h2","heading_alignment":"right","show_border":false,"row_background":false,"collapsible":true,"show_view_all":false,"view_all_position":"top","button_link":"","open_new_window":false,"background_color_light":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","background_color_dark":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","enable_microdata_schema":false,"desktop_layout":"1","image_alignment":"left","desktop_height":"400px","show_section_divider":false,"make_full_page_width":false,"padding_top":28,"padding_bottom":28,"image_alignment_mobile":"left","mobile_height":"2