","blocks":{"frequently_asked_question_Rww3Hg":{"type":"frequently_asked_question","settings":{"icon":"none","another_icon":"","custom_icon":"","heading":"How long does delivery take?","row_content":"<p>Orders are usually delivered within <strong>2–5 working days<\/strong> depending on your location. You’ll receive tracking details once your order is dispatched.<\/p>"}},"frequently_asked_question_HKNYyg":{"type":"frequently_asked_question","settings":{"icon":"none","another_icon":"","custom_icon":"","heading":"How much does delivery cost?","row_content":"<p>Delivery fees are calculated at checkout based on your area and order size. Orders over a certain amount may qualify for<strong> free delivery<\/strong>— look out for promotions!<\/p>"}},"frequently_asked_question_7TKqQz":{"type":"frequently_asked_question","settings":{"icon":"none","another_icon":"","custom_icon":"","heading":"Do you deliver nationwide?","row_content":"<p>Yes, we deliver across South Africa. For remote or outlying areas, delivery may take a little longer.<\/p>"}},"frequently_asked_question_QBfMn8":{"type":"frequently_asked_question","settings":{"icon":"none","another_icon":"","custom_icon":"","heading":"Can I collect my order?","row_content":"<p>Yes, collection is available at our factory shop or designated pickup points. You’ll receive a notification when your order is ready for collection.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["frequently_asked_question_Rww3Hg","frequently_asked_question_HKNYyg","frequently_asked_question_7TKqQz","frequently_asked_question_QBfMn8"],"name":"t:sections.question_and_answer.name","settings":{"heading":"DELIVERY & SHIPPING","highlight_type":"underline","heading_size":100,"heading_tag":"h2","heading_alignment":"right","show_border":false,"row_background":false,"collapsible":true,"show_view_all":false,"view_all_position":"top","button_link":"","open_new_window":false,"background_color_light":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","background_color_dark":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","enable_microdata_schema":false,"d